OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a dry start a band of wet
OL,6,Fand rather breezy weather will feed
OL,7,Feastwards across the region this
OL,8,Fmorning. The rain will turn showery
OL,9,Fthis afternoon, with sunnier weather
OL,10,Fdeveloping later. The brisk winds will
OL,11,Fease a little too.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny lingering rain will soon
OL,14,Fclear in the east, leaving a generally
OL,15,Fdry night with clear spells. The
OL,16,Fbreeze will continue to ease, and it
OL,17,Fwill stay frost-free.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
