OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA day of sunshine and well
OL,6,Fscattered, mostly light showers is
OL,7,Fexpected on Saturday. Feeling fresher
OL,8,Fthanks to a west to northwesterly
OL,9,Fbreeze, though pleasant when the sun
OL,10,Fappears.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FAfter a
OL,13,Fchilly start Sunday looks likely to be
OL,14,Fdry with some sunshine. Feeling cooler
OL,15,Fon Monday and Tuesday as a
OL,16,Fnortheasterly breeze introduces more
OL,17,Fcloud and the odd shower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
